org.stringmatching.hybrid.ahocorasick_wumanber

Class AC_WM_Pattern

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.stringmatching.pattern.PatternModel
      • org.stringmatching.hybrid.ahocorasick_wumanber.AC_WM_Pattern
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, IPatternModel

    public class AC_WM_Pattern
extends PatternModel
implements java.io.Serializable
    Build the the Pattern Model for the hybrid method.

    According to the predefined max length for Aho-Corasick patterns model, the patterns are splitter to build the Aho-Corasick and the Wu Manber patterns model
